const sensor = require('../sensor');
const datetime = require('../datetime');
const common = require('../common');
const base = require('./base');
const reservoir = require('./reservoir');

export function createSensors() {

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '-',   //
      part: 'realtime-data-gateSeepage',       //realtimedata
      category: '',
      id: 'HHSK000100020001000FF0',
      name: '',
      unit: 'm',
      limit: datetime.isFloodDate() ? '' : '',
      max: datetime.isFloodDate() ? base.getBaseInfo().floodWaterLevel : base.getBaseInfo().highWaterLevel,
      tag: 'water-level',
      index: 0,
      high: 190,
      low: 100,
      image: 'water-level'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', part: 'realtime', name: '', unit: 'mm',
      limit: '', max: 3,
      tag: 'dam-accumulate-down', image: 'flood-discharge'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', part: 'realtime', name: '', unit: 'mm/h',
      limit: '', max: 3, value: -common.BOUNDARY,
      tag: 'dam-accumulate-down-speed', image: 'flood-discharge'
    }),
    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', part: 'realtime', name: 'K',
      limit: 'K', max: 1.3, value: common.BOUNDARY,
      tag: 'stability-argument', image: 'flood-discharge'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', part: 'realtime', name: 'J',
      limit: 'J', min: 3, value: common.BOUNDARY,
      tag: 'seepage-slope', image: 'flood-discharge'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', category: '1#', part: 'realtime', name: '',
      limit: '', max: 3, unit: 'mm',
      tag: 'gate-accumulate-down', image: 'discharge-water'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', category: '1#', part: 'realtime', name: '',

      tag: 'gate-accumulate-down-speed', image: 'discharge-water'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', category: '1#', part: 'realtime', name: '',
      limit: '', max: 0.6, min: 0, unit: '',
      tag: 'pier-inclination', image: 'discharge-water'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', category: '1#', part: 'realtime', name: 'K',
      limit: 'K', value: common.BOUNDARY, min: 1.08,
      tag: 'stability-coefficient', image: 'discharge-water'

    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', category: '1#', part: 'realtime', name: '',
      limit: '', value: common.BOUNDARY, max: 3.00, unit: 'g',
      tag: 'gate-vibration-severity', image: 'discharge-water'
    }),
    sensor.createSensor({
      section: '', part: 'realtime', name: 'K',
      limit: 'K', value: common.BOUNDARY, min: 1.08,
      tag: 'shaft-factor', image: 'discharge-water'

      part: 'data', name: '', section: '', value: common.BOUNDARY, id: 'HHSK000100030001000100',
      unit: 'v', tag: 'voltage', image: 'storage-capacity', category: ''

    sensor.createSensor({
      part: 'data', section: '', name: '', value: common.BOUNDARY,
      unit: '', high: 360, low: 0, tag: 'wind-direction', image: 'storage-capacity', category: ''
    }),
    sensor.createSensor({
      part: 'data',
      section: '',
      id: 'HHSK000100020001000FF0',
      bias: function (value) {
        return reservoir.getRelations().getCapacityRelationShip('capacity', value)
      },
      name: '',
      unit: 'm',
      tag: 'storage-capacity',
      image: 'storage-capacity',
      category: ''
    }),
    sensor.createSensor({
      part: 'data', section: '', name: '', id: 'HHSK000100020001000FF0',
